e first which caught the attention of a lot of people in technology sphere.\r\n<h3>Recognition</h3>\r\nThis app was featured on the Facebook developer blog and was also featured on quite a few online newspapers and blogs.\r\n\r\nAdditional\r\n\r\nThe site has undergone a design overhaul since we launched it back in 2010 but its still up and running: <a title="Ulive facebook app" href="https://apps.facebook.com/tvnz-ulive/" target="_blank">https://apps.facebook.com/tvnz-ulive/</a>', 'Ulive', 'This project encompassed a wide range of web technologies. It was the first facebook app to allow users to interact with live television and was featured on facebook''s developer blog.', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '337-revision-26', '', '', '2013-01-13 13:13:23', '2013-01-13 01:13:23', '', 337, 'http://localhost/techblog/articles/337-revision-26/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
